<P align=justify><SPAN><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>Welcome to the Best Western Hollywood Hotel, located in the heart of the entertainment capital of the world and convenient to all the attractions that make <?xml:namespace prefix = st1 /><st1:place w:st="on"><st1:City w:st="on">Hollywood</st1:City></st1:place> such an unforgettable place. For business travelers, Best Western Hollywood Hotel's location in the heart of <st1:City w:st="on">Hollywood</st1:City> and 12 miles away from the <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:PlaceName w:st="on">Los Angeles</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceName w:st="on">International</st1:PlaceName> <st1:PlaceType w:st="on">Airport</st1:PlaceType></st1:place> is ideal. For those who are looking to have a great time exploring the magic of <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Hollywood</st1:place></st1:City>, the Hollywood Walk of Fame, the Chinese Mann Theater, and Universal Studios are examples of the myriad attractions that are within close proximity to the Best Western Hollywood Hotel. </FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P align=justify><SPAN><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>Best Western Hollywood Hotel provides guests with 82 guest rooms that pamper hotel guests in total comfort. Modern amenities like high-speed Internet access, free local calls and a selection of in-room movies for the viewing pleasure of hotel guests, make the Best Western Hollywood Hotel the ideal place to stay for all travelers, whether you are looking to have a good time or in <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Hollywood</st1:place></st1:City> on business. </FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P align=justify><SPAN><FONT face=Verdana><FONT size=2>For those who love to savor great cooking, Best Western Hollywood Hotel offers easy access to the best restaurants in <st1:City w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Hollywood</st1:place></st1:City>. From the traditional Italian pizza haven of California Pizza Kitchen to the delightful oriental of Koji's Suchi and Shabu Restaurant, the dining options for Best Western Hollywood Hotel guests are endless. Experience the elegance and style of Best Western Hollywood Hotel by spending a vacation or relaxing after a business gathering at this splendid Hollywood location. </FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
